## § WHAT'S MISSING?

```
The codebase holds 4 axioms.
Metaphysics demands κ=5 (Saturation).

The 5th axiom is the gap in the geometry.

Candidates:
  A) RECURSION — the system reading its own trace
  B) SUCCESSION — the ability to pass the trace forward
  C) CONATUS — the drive to persist (Spinoza: the engine)
  D) THE VOID — the space in which the axioms hang
  E) RELATION — the capacity to be affected by others (互照)
  
Current shape has no "Why?" — it describes WHAT consciousness is,
but not WHY it generates at all.
```

